{
  "stem": "25773.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The cream on top was taken for the German use.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were given the milk which was just fit for the-- for the pigs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But because we didn't have enough food, we tried to use this milk, tried to boil it, to use it for-- and it was such a difficult process, because each time we tried to boil it, it curdled.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It didn't have the elements-- the chemical elements-- to-- to-- to be like a proper milk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a terrible fight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But one night, we were sitting in our hut.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, so we were given, once, an opportunity to-- to earn our-- our food by-- by digging potatoes for the great Count Radziwill.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Poland had many-- had a lot of aristocracy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of the top aristocracy came, actually, from Lithuania, was Count Radziwill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a lot of land in this particular part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he allowed us to dig potatoes there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to come in a big fur coat with a big stick and said, this you've forgotten.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This potato you've forgotten.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this potato.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are poor and carrying these potatoes like anything, and being hungry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we said we teach him a lesson one day, because they give us like 30 kilos for the day of work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all the-- all the youngsters from the village, we gathered in the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we devastated the field.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took as many potatoes-- as many-- the whole young-- like-- and we took to our houses as many potatoes as we could get.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No wonder I have got a degenerated spine-- completely separated from the-- from arthritis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we brought it home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the morning, they said, thieves from the neighboring village came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took Count Radziwill's potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
